      "text": "vicinity of Twin Falls, Idaho, on or about August 19, 1947. Colonel [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "at that time indicated to Mr. [REDACTED] that he would check with the Army area",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "in order to ascertain whether or not they were conducting any experiments in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "this vicinity at that time.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Colonel [REDACTED] has subsequently advised Mr. [REDACTED] that he has",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "been advised by the Army area that no such experiments were being conducted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
